high_descs: Go to the wall, turn right, and go to the curved counter.
Take the butter knife from the curved counter.
Turn left, turn right, and go to the other side of the curved counter.
Slice the apple on the curved counter.
Turn right, turn around, turn right, and go to the dishwasher.
Put the knife on the counter above the dishwasher.
Turn around, go to the wall, turn right, and go to the curved counter.
Take a slice of apple from the curved counter.
Turn right, go toward the wall, turn left, and go to the sink.
Put the apple slice in the sink, run the water in the sink, turn off the water, and take the apple from the sink.
Turn left, go to the dishwasher, and turn right.
Put the apple next to the butter knife on the counter above the dishwasher.
anns.task_desc: Put a slice of apple with a butter knife above the dishwasher.

high_descs: Move to the right to face the end of the white counter top.
Pick the knife up from off of the white counter top.
Move to the right to face the other side of the white counter top.
Slice the red apple into 3 slices.
Move to the right and walk around the counter top to face the counter next to the microwave.
Place the knife on the counter top.
Turn around and walk to the right around the white counter top.
Pick up a slice of the apple.
Move to the right, walk around the counter top and go straight to face the sink.
Place the apple slice in the sink, fill it up with water, drain the water, and pick up the apple slice.
Move to the left to face the counter to the right of the microwave.
Place the apple slice on the counter top.
anns.task_desc: Place the rinsed apple slice on the counter top to the right of the microwave.

high_descs: Turn right, move to the counter near the knife.
Pick up the knife near the edge of the counter.
Turn left, move to the counter near the black stool.
Slice the apple in to sections.
Turn right, move to the counter at the dishwasher.
Put the knife on the counter.
Turn right, move to the counter near the black stool.
Pick up a section of apple.
Turn right, move to the counter in front of the sink.
Put the apple section into the sink, rinse it, pick it back up.
Turn left, move to the counter at the dishwasher.
Put the apple section on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed apple section on the counter.
